               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa ʾardǝʾt “Book of the Disciples” (fols. 2r-34r) (cp. A.Z.
                     AESCOLY, Recueil de Textes Falachas, Paris 1951, pp. 82-149)
 II)
                     Miscellaneous hymns and prayers (fols. 34v-67v) 
 III) Maṣḥafa malāʾǝkt
                     “Book of the Angels” (fols. 67v-80r)
 IV) Sǝmʿu wa-lǝbbǝw ʾo-daqiqa ʾAddām
                     “Listen and understand O children of Adam...” (fols. 80r-85v)
 V) Gadla
                     ʾAbrǝhām “Vita of Abrǝham”, (fols. 85v-88r), incomplete 
 VI) Ya-sabʿǝt
                     sanbat ṣalot “The Liturgy of the Seventh Sabbath”, (fols. 88r-91v), incomplete
                     (cp. M.Devens, The Liturgy of the Seventh Sabbath, Wiesbaden 1995, pp.
                     152-155)
 VII) Nagar baʾǝnta aśartu qālāt “Story of the Ten
                     Commandments...” (fols. 91v-94r).</summary>
                  
